{"tid":1819092,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(請share,一齊做) 韓國瑜當選既話 唔再去台灣","createTime":"2020-01-10T13:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T16:45:38.000Z","uid":44074,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51b3b732066a636ee819bb320561a32642abfc32","tid":1819092,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:07:20.000Z","msg":"比佢當選既話 <br />\n容乜易為咗獻媚<br />\n每次入境都人面識別捉手足去大陸送中<br />\n如果係為咗經濟嘅話<br />\n自己諗下訪台旅客香港人比例有幾多<br />\n淨係一個丁屎咁多大嘅城市已經佔成個中國嘅一半<br />\n仲要諗下真正消費嘅係香港人定係嗰啲大陸人<br />\n選左件奶共撚出嚟 我就唔敢去台灣啦<br />\n區議會選區見到黃絲起碼佔香港一半<br />\n未計投唔到票嘅後生黃絲<br />\n可以參考一下開放左自由行既香港變得污煙漳氣<br />\n呢個就係韓國瑜當選一年之後嘅境況<br />\n變到大陸咁 咁我做乜唔返深圳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yy3TDCp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYy3TDCp.png&h=ebd1bdad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6bc9f5490ca01ad3345eb62bf309ae1585d1b9e","tid":1819092,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:08:17.000Z","msg":"share比啲為咗開放中國旅客去台灣先投條奶共垃圾既人thanks!"},{"pid":"bd7df089621033d74948b719675a1fe576e4b3b2","tid":1819092,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ae622c36f3dad791b1194409b3906cec26c3db1","tid":1819092,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd7df089621033d74948b719675a1fe576e4b3b2","tid":1819092,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"佢由day1已經親中 急不及待要賣台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/782k26Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F782k26Z.jpg&h=b8f3d95a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a42ad55ea78da5dde9a93910d34942ac4f267edb","tid":1819092,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c540f81d3efdf7cdeddcdc8c59a616ef13298517","tid":1819092,"uid":90499,